name: Royal Air Force A330-243MRTT [ZZ338] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
The RAF A330s are a common sight at YYC during the summer, and as the Brits wrap up their annual training at CFB Suffield, we get quite a few around this time of year. Here we have ZZ338, one of ten A332s in their fleet arriving runway 17L from Brize Norton, UK! ATC is included, enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
